'''塞伯汉航空5915号班机空难'''发生于2014年8月10日，[[伊朗|伊朗]][[塞伯汉航空|塞伯汉航空]]的一架载有48人的小型客机于当地时间9点45分在[[德黑兰|德黑兰]][[梅赫拉巴德机场|梅赫拉巴德机场]]坠毁。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2014/08-10/6477751.shtml|title=一架小型客机在伊朗首都坠毁 造成至少40人遇难|publisher=中国新闻网|accessdate=2014-08-10|archive-date=2017-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171013220642/http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2014/08-10/6477751.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>机上载有40名乘客(包括7名儿童)与8名机组人员。<ref name="RT1">[http://rt.com/news/179252-tehran-airport-plane-crash/ Passenger plane crashes near Tehran's Mehrabad airport - Iranian media] {{Wayback|url=http://rt.com/news/179252-tehran-airport-plane-crash/ |date=20171128125709 }} RT. 10 August 2014</ref>目击者称，飞机起飞后仅在空中停留几秒钟就冲向地面。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.qq.com/a/20140810/017128.htm|title=目击者：客机起飞后在空中停留几秒钟就冲向地面|publisher=腾讯新闻|accessdate=2014-08-10|archive-date=2014-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140812230342/http://news.qq.com/a/20140810/017128.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 事情經過 ==
飞机失事后，撞向[[德黑兰|德黑兰]]西部米娜·格拉斯大道一幢住宅，现场浓烟滚滚。[[伊朗伊斯兰共和国通讯社|伊朗伊斯兰共和国通讯社]]声称飞机[[引擎故障|引擎故障]]<ref name=avh>{{cite web|last1=Hradecky|first1=Simon|title=Crash: Sepahan A140 at Tehran on Aug 10th 2014, lost height after takeoff|url=http://avherald.com/h?article=47897aae&opt=0|website=The Aviation Herald|accessdate=2014-08-10|date=2014-08-10|archive-date=2017-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171117081225/http://avherald.com/h?article=47897aae&opt=0|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 机组乘客 ==
该班机有40名乘客，8名机组人员，乘客包括34名成人和6名儿童<ref name=RT>{{cite news|title=About 40 killed as airliner crashes near Tehran's Mehrabad airport (video)|url=http://rt.com/news/179252-tehran-airport-plane-crash/|accessdate=2014-08-10|publisher=RT|date=2014-08-10|archive-date=2017-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171128125709/https://www.rt.com/news/179252-tehran-airport-plane-crash/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。国营媒体最初报道无人幸存<ref>{{cite news|last1=News|first1=Arab|title=Passenger Plane Crashes Near Tehran Airport|url=https://plus.google.com/+arabnews/posts/arpVbfRXaSG|accessdate=2014-08-10|archive-date=2016-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160414005937/https://plus.google.com/+arabnews/posts/arpVbfRXaSG|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但后来又称有10名幸存者。

==起因==
[[法尔斯通讯社|法尔斯通讯社]]援引伊朗机场公司高管穆罕默德的声明，称“该航班一引擎失效，导致其坠毁于德黑兰-卡拉奇高速公路北侧。幸存者讲述二号发动机在起飞时已停止<ref name=aje>{{cite news|title=Iran plane crash kills dozens|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2014/08/iran-plane-crash-20148106119908678.html|accessdate=2014-08-10|publisher=Al Jazeera|date=2014-08-10|archive-date=2018-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180801074158/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2014/08/iran-plane-crash-20148106119908678.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”据报道，起飞4分钟后出现技术问题，飞机员返航，但无法保持高度最终坠毁<ref>{{cite web |url=http://avherald.com/h?article=47897aae&opt=0 |title=Crash: Sepahan A140 at Tehran on Aug 10th 2014, lost height after takeoff |publisher=Avherald.com |date= |accessdate=2014-08-16 |archive-date=2017-11-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171117081225/http://avherald.com/h?article=47897aae&opt=0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[安东诺夫140客机|安东诺夫140客机]]是最近期开发的，事故班机在伊朗完成组装，2007年交付使用<ref>{{cite web|author1=Gladman, Paul|title=Antonov An-140|url=http://www.flightglobal.com/blogs/aircraft-pictures/2007/12/antonov-an140/|publisher=Flightglobal|accessdate=2014-08-11|date=2007-12-19|archive-date=2014-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141011004351/http://www.flightglobal.com/blogs/aircraft-pictures/2007/12/antonov-an140/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.ce.cn/aero/201410/16/t20141016_3716594.shtml |title=《大飞机》：2014空难频发为哪般？_航空产业_中国经济网 |accessdate=2021-12-17 |archive-date=2021-12-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211217022307/http://www.ce.cn/aero/201410/16/t20141016_3716594.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

